But the superior merit of Agricola soon occasioned his removal from the government of Britain and forever disappointed this rational , though extensive scheme of conquest . 
Before his departure , the prudent general had provided for security as well as for dominion . 
He had observed , that the island is almost divided into two unequal parts by the opposite gulfs , or , as they are now called , the Friths of Scotland . 
This wall of Antoninus , at a small distance beyond the modern cities of Edinburgh and Glasgow , was fixed as the limit of the Roman province . 
The native Caledonians preserved , in the northern extremity of the island , their wild independence , for which they were not less indebted to their poverty than to their valor . 
Their incursions were frequently repelled and chastised but their country was never subdued . 
