It is a just though trite observation , that victorious Rome was herself subdued by the arts of Greece . 
Those immortal writers who still command the admiration of modern Europe , soon became the favorite object of study and imitation in Italy and the western provinces . 
But the elegant amusements of the Romans were not suffered to interfere with their sound maxims of policy . 
