The family of Herod , at least after it had been favored by fortune , was lineally descended from Cimon and Miltiades , Theseus and Cecrops , Aeacus and Jupiter . 
But the posterity of so many gods and heroes was fallen into the most abject state . 
According to the rigor of the law , the emperor might have asserted his claim , and the prudent Atticus prevented , by a frank confession , the officiousness of informers . 
But the equitable Nerva , who then filled the throne , refused to accept any part of it , and commanded him to use , without scruple , the present of fortune . 
The cautious Athenian still insisted , that the treasure was too considerable for a subject , and that he knew not how to use it . 
