Such was the deserved fate of a brutal savage , destitute , as he has generally been represented , of every sentiment that distinguishes a civilized , or even a human being . 
The body was suited to the soul . 
The stature of Maximin exceeded the measure of eight feet , and circumstances almost incredible are related of his matchless strength and appetite . 
