His birth was obscure , and the obscurity equally gave room to the aspersions of his enemies , and the flattery of his adherents . 
If we credit the scandal of the former , Artaxerxes sprang from the illegitimate commerce of a tanner's wife with a common soldier . 
The latter represent him as descended from a branch of the ancient kings of Persian , though time and misfortune had gradually reduced his ancestors to the humble station of private citizens . 
The Parthians were defeated in three great battles . 
In the last of these their king Artaban was slain , and the spirit of the nation was forever broken . 
The authority of Artaxerxes was solemnly acknowledged in a great assembly held at Balch in Khorasan . 
