Westward of the Goths , the numerous tribes of the Vandals were spread along the banks of the Oder , and the sea coast of Pomerania and Mecklenburgh . 
A striking resemblance of manners , complexion , religion , and language , seemed to indicate that the Vandals and the Goths were originally one great people . 
The latter appear to have been subdivided into Ostrogoths , Visigoths , and Gepidae . 
