The Romans had long experienced the daring valor of the people of Lower Germany . 
The union of their strength threatened Gaul with a more formidable invasion , and required the presence of Gallienus , the heir and colleague of Imperial power . 
The treacherous language of panegyrics and medals darkly announces a long series of victories . 
