He reigned four or five years over Gaul , Spain , and Britain , the slave and sovereign of a licentious army , whom he dreaded , and by whom he was despised . 
The valor and fortune of Aurelian at length opened the prospect of a deliverance . 
He ventured to disclose his melancholy situation , and conjured the emperor to hasten to the relief of his unhappy rival . 
