The Persians expressed their desire of being introduced to the presence of the Roman emperor . 
They were at length conducted to a soldier , who was seated on the grass . 
A piece of stale bacon and a few hard peas composed his supper . 
A coarse woollen garment of purple was the only circumstance that announced his dignity . 
